Customer reviews knowledge base

Self-service support

   The knowledge base articles and tutorials will help you to get up and
   running with Trusted Shops customer reviews. If you don’t find what you
   are looking for, simply give us a ring or drop us an email.

Getting Started

   Find everything you need to start getting better reviews.

Integrate Trustbadge^®

   Integrate your Trustbadge^® within minutes. Show your seller rating and
   stars to your customers and get a continuous stream of incoming
   reviews.

Collect Reviews

   Fully automated or web-based without integration, straight away or
   later - you can collect reviews in various ways.

Show Reviews

   Trustbadge^® Technology, Public Review Profile, Review Sticker and how
   to embed everything properly.

Manage Reviews

   Always be up-to-date, reply to comments and show you that you care for
   your customers.

Google Seller Rating

   How to create more visibility on Google, how to show your stars
   automatically.

Software integration

   Using Magento, Shopify, ePages or similar? Find simple how-to's and
   plug-ins.

Product reviews

   More visitors, higher conversion rates, fewer returns.

Traffic Package

   More visitors and customer loyalty. You are just a few clicks away from
   starting your own campaigns.

