Integration of the Trusted Shops Trustbadge

   To display our ratings collected, the Trusted Shops Trustbadge is
   integrated on some of our websites.

   Pursuant to art. 6 para. 1 sentence 1 lit. f GDPR, this serves to
   safeguard our legitimate interests in the optimal marketing of our
   offer that are overriding in the process of balancing of interests. The
   Trustbadge and the services advertised with it are an offer of Trusted
   Shops GmbH, Subbelrather Str. 15C, 50823 Cologne.

   When the Trustbadge is called, the web server automatically saves a
   so-called server log file, which contains e.g. your IP address, date
   and time of the call, transferred data volume and the requesting
   provider (access data) and documents the call. This access data is not
   evaluated and is automatically overwritten at the latest seven days
   after the end of your page visit.
